model_explanation: the focus in S1 is on both the recipient (ROB) and the item (ORANGES). This means Sam gave oranges to Rob and no other item to him, and didn’t give oranges to anyone else. S2 states that Sam didn’t give Rob apples, which is consistent with S1. The claim in S1 thus entails S2.
